<p>Hi <%= @user.name %>,</p>

<p>
  We received a request to reset the password for your Activity Finder account
  (<%= @user.email %>).
</p>

<p>
  <a href="<%= @reset_url %>" style="display:inline-block;padding:10px 20px;background:#0d6efd;color:#fff;text-decoration:none;border-radius:5px;font-weight:bold;">
    Reset my password
  </a>
</p>

<p>This link expires in <strong>15 minutes</strong>.</p>

<p>
  If the button above doesn't work, copy and paste this URL into your browser:<br>
  <a href="<%= @reset_url %>"><%= @reset_url %></a>
</p>

<p>If you didn't request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email — your password will not change.</p>

<p>— The Activity Finder team</p>
